@laanwj The work happened in #5582, this was just pulling the trigger.

Thinking on this a little more, we should document pretty loudly that 10.6 will not be supported for 0.11. It'd be helpful to add to the 0.10 release notes something like : "OSX 10.6 support is deprecated and will be completely removed in 0.11."

I'll also add a change so that configure fails if building against <10.7.
